data.description: This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is a gem, offering the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and leisure. Nestled in a prime location near a toll road, it provides easy access to major transportation routes, making commuting a breeze. Whether you're a busy professional who needs a quick commute, a family seeking a clean and spacious sanctuary, or someone who loves the idea of having a community pool within walking distance, this home has it all. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own and experience the comfort and convenience it has to offer. Home warranty included with home. Schedule a showing today!
